title: Senator Huff to Receive Lifetime Achievement Award (California Senate Republican Caucus)
text: ( Source : California Senate Republican Caucus ) Senator Bob Huff (R-San Dimas ) will receive one of the most prestigious awards issued by the California Building Industry Association ( CBIA ) during the Annual Leadership Recognition Dinner
